{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "破冰", "storyInfo": "被軟禁的恩希亞在極光的幫助下決定去找姐姐。\n聖山大殿中，恩雅與大長老一番交鋒，為自己贏得了未來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g10_manorhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......切斯特叔叔，為什麼我不能出去？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總裁吩咐了，在他回來之前，不允許你四處跑。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那老哥什麼時候回來？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總裁現在應當正在前往聖山的路上，過兩天就能回來了。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想去散步也不行嗎？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是在宅子附近的話......我會派人跟著你。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞，現在謝拉格的形勢十分險峻，這也是為了你好。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老哥......你就一定要這麼做嗎？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我該怎麼辦......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極光？！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓——好嚴密的守備，我好不容易才進來的。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是和Sharp隊長一起去博士那邊了嗎？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我這次來，就是博士有話要我帶給你。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，阿克托斯在領地內集結了大量士兵，但是，這支隊伍的領導者是那位博士，而不是阿克托斯。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯人呢？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不清楚......根據眼線的回報，在將這支隊伍的指揮權正式交給博士後，他就不知所蹤了。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那個博士的隊伍是誘餌？不，不會這麼簡單。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "規模呢？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契領地響應阿克托斯號召的家族和您想像的差不多，以此估算的話——阿克托斯應該不可能再集結起另外一支同樣規模的隊伍。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是他不可能待在後方，有另一支隊伍的可能性很大。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契家的戰士本來就很擅長在山野中行動，這確實不是沒有可能。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，無論是誘餌還是主力，這支隊伍都不能放任不理。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓魏斯傳令，命戰士們在山下集結，等候命令。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後派人去盯著大部隊，你主要負責去找出阿克托斯的蹤跡。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......希望我能登上聖山，潛入蔓珠院去找姐姐？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士的意思是，如今，佩爾羅契家和希瓦艾什家之間的衝突已經幾乎無法避免了。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，如果說還有一個人可以阻止這一切的話，那麼，這個人必然是你的姐姐，當代聖女，恩雅·希瓦艾什。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#5$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本，博士是想秉承羅德島不干政的方針，選擇袖手旁觀的。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，博士指出一點，既然還政對於恩希歐迪斯先生來說只是一個幌子，那麼他也必然不會將對謝拉格的信仰放在眼中。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而一旦希瓦艾什家的部隊真的擊敗了佩爾羅契家的部隊，那麼對他來說，阻攔他將謝拉格納入囊中的，也就只有蔓珠院。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是謝拉格人民的信仰對象，聖女。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士說，他並不是想要讓你去說服聖女做些什麼，而是你曾經拜託過他，希望他能夠幫忙緩和你們兄妹之間關係。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他對於自己來到謝拉格後沒有幫上忙一直感到有些自責。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這怎麼能怪博士！我才要對博士和隨行的各位道歉，明明應該是一次愉快的旅行，結果卻因為老哥而變成了這個樣子......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也不怪你呀，崖心。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，博士的意思是，他可以不在乎很多東西，但一方面他從一開始就被恩希歐迪斯先生捲了進來。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方面，你是恩希歐迪斯先生的妹妹也是不爭的事實。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，博士還是打算做一些什麼。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓你上山，是希望你能成為聖女身邊的保險。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士希望我在必要的時候去阻止老哥。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者在必要的時候帶著聖女逃跑。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞下意識地摸了摸自己手中的繩環。"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是小時候，姐姐親手為她編織的。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#2$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一次潛入行動，我和其他的隨行幹員會一起協助你。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有更好的辦法。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家只要能幫我到達聖山腳下就好，剩下的，交給我一個人。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，為什麼你要把行軍的速度控制得這麼慢？", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#3$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "要讓觀察著我們的眼睛再多欣賞欣賞。;現在還不能快。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line155", "option2": "line155"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，古羅你該不會還沒搞清楚我們要幹什麼吧？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不就是吸引希瓦艾什家的注意嗎？我就是覺得有點太慢了。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你就是想直接衝過去和希瓦艾什家打一仗。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那當然。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前被瓦萊絲壓了一頭，我現在胸口憋著一口氣呢。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#2$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，在大典上被抓走的尤卡坦的位置確認了。", "name": "佩爾羅契家戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和您想的一樣，沒有被帶回希瓦艾什家的領地，而是就近關在了山腳下的鎮子裡。", "name": "佩爾羅契家戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "辛苦了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line175"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你可真厲害啊，這麼短的時間裡就能摸清楚尤卡坦老爺被關押的位置。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#4$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，這點情報收集，我布朗陶家的人也做得到。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，既然確認了尤卡坦的位置，我和這個傻大個也該動起來了吧？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#3$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是的。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line185"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#5$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沉默什麼？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#10$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼，原來你在喊我嗎？我可不是傻大個！", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#6$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深呼吸）", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古羅！將軍！哼......這樣就行了吧？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問你，你知道你要做什麼吧？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，去最近的車站搞點破壞，讓你有機會去救你丈夫。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#4$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道就好。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "替博士警告你一句，別真的搞出人命來。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，車站裡都是些平民百姓，我古羅是絕不會對他們出手的。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#2$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，博士，要是希瓦艾什家的人真來了——", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能說，我會儘量留手。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g10_manorhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "崖心，你說你要找的......是你的登山設備？", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，你要攀登喀蘭聖山？", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......按照你說的，現在別說聖山上，聖山下肯定也有很多人了。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果要從正面上聖山，就算是Sharp隊長大概也很難潛進去。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這可難不倒我~", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能到達山腳下，剩下的交給我就好。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......這樣的話，我和其他人就不能保護你了。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事沒事。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也在羅德島接受過許多訓練，一般的對手我還是應付得過來的。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可......", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#4$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_275", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞，你要去哪？", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#4$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切斯特叔叔......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想要去登山。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要去登哪座山？", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀蘭聖山。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡即將成為戰場，你過去會受傷的。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要去那裡幹什麼？", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切斯特叔叔，自從我愛上登山之後，我就一直想要用自己的雙手爬上喀蘭聖山看看。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從姐姐成為聖女離我們而去之後，這想法就越來越強烈......總有一天，我要爬上它的頂峰，把姐姐接回家。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，這個機會來了。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做不到的，恩希亞。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......即使我做不到把姐姐帶回家，至少在這個時候，我也要陪在姐姐身邊。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老哥做了這麼多的事，姐姐一定也很迷茫。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有辦法阻止老哥，那麼，至少，我要陪在姐姐的身邊！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#9$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧拉維爾，你最小的女兒，也已經長大了。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_286_1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二小姐，抱歉，老爺的命令是，為了您的安全著想，不允許您離開這座宅邸。", "name": "希瓦艾什家士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......停手吧。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸。", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切斯特叔叔！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#3$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切斯特經理，你這是違抗老爺的命令！", "name": "希瓦艾什家士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡發生的事一切責任由我承擔。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#6$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......雖然你都這麼說了，可是二小姐她的安危......", "name": "希瓦艾什家士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希瓦艾什家的人，從來不會冒無謂的風險。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，就相信她吧。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......好吧。", "name": "希瓦艾什家士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，為二小姐和幾位羅德島的客人準備最好的馱獸。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了。", "name": "希瓦艾什家士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_286_1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，切斯特叔叔！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_422_aurora_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您，切斯特經理。", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#9$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直以為您......", "name": "極光"}, "figure_art": "avg_422_aurora_1#9$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必謝我。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，時間緊迫。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意安全。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好！", "name": "恩希亞"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧拉維爾。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你和伊莉莎白死後，我一直後悔，過去應該支持你對領地的改革，而不是與你作對。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，當你兒子想要繼承你的理想時，我選擇了毫無保留地支持他。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯他做得很好。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅作為聖女也得到了謝拉格人的愛戴。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞雖然得了礦石病，但她的病情得到了抑制，而且一如既往地開朗。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#3$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_267_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我剛才忽然反應過來。", "name": "切斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_267_1#6$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有多久沒有見到這三個孩子聚在一起，露出兄妹之間應有的笑容了呢？"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老，您應當好好休息......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照記錄，這座大殿，是在三族議會成立後，三族的人民共同建造的。三族人民的存在與合作要遠遠早於現代三族制度的建立。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，過了上千年，中間修修補補，最終成了現在的樣子。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這張椅子，也在這裡擺了上千年。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有十幾位大長老坐在這張椅子上面，度過了他們的一生。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......就好像，有十幾位聖女，都在這座山上鬱鬱而終。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從一開始，聖女就是蔓珠院為了方便信仰傳播而捏造出來的。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老在這個時候提及我早就知道的事實，難道是想說，信仰是虛假的？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的話也直接起來了，但事情恰恰相反，恩雅，不，聖女。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女，咳咳，你知道老朽的名字嗎？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不知道。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座蔓珠院中，恐怕已經沒人記得了。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連老朽自己，都已經忘了。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一任的大長老，在接過上一任的衣缽之後，都會只成為大長老。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將來，人們也會忘記你的名字，只知道你叫作聖女。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，大長老和聖女都會發現——", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們信仰的，並非耶拉岡德。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們可以信仰任何東西，只要一個故事，一些巧合，他們就會信仰你，信仰我，信仰恩希歐迪斯，信仰山，信仰水，甚至信仰一片樹葉。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然人們什麼都可以信仰，那麼信仰究竟是什麼？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老們最終得出了答案：", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們信仰的，是信仰本身。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們將選擇權交給信仰的對象。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#2$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們將自己排斥的事物統統歸咎於信仰。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#2$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們無條件地信任著信仰所指導的生活方式。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#2$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以信仰是什麼？", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#2$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰是懶惰，是逃避，是頹廢！信仰是安定，信仰是停滯！咳咳咳咳咳——", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#4$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您該休息了，大長老。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，聖女，聖女！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#4$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 20.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大長老倏地抓住恩雅的手腕。"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "力道之大，在恩雅的皮膚上都留下了紅印，彷彿把他畢生的力量都用在了這上面。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的雙眼盯著眼前的聖女，卻彷彿在看著別人。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$stranger_intro", "key": "$stranger_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰醜惡！但即使如此，沒有人能夠摧毀信仰！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格歷經千年，三大家族之間隔閡漸深，卻無人能夠否定信仰，信仰是謝拉格之所以是謝拉格的根基！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰將謝拉格人統合在了一起，人們追求信仰，人們依賴信仰！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格由此存在了千年！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們渴望安定，人們渴望停滯！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯以為他贏了，他沒有，他不可能贏。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他憑什麼戰勝謝拉格這千年以來凝聚而成的信仰！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老朽已經要不行了，但你還年輕，你是這蔓珠院的聖女，你也將成為這蔓珠院的大長老。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去教會他，去戰勝他，讓他明白，信仰面前，他的那些動作不值一提！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#6$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅沉默片刻，卻將大長老的手硬生生地從自己手腕上掰開。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 20.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的眼中有著對眼前老人的憐憫，更多的，卻是堅決。"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不同意，大長老。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說信仰意味著停滯，人們依賴信仰，是因為他們渴望安定。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不這麼認為。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠然，人一旦有所信仰，總會習慣性地依賴信仰。懶惰、逃避、頹廢......您說的這些，我不否認。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這絕不是說，信仰意味著停滯。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰就是信仰，信仰本身是沒有屬性的，信仰的內容是被賦予的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰向前走，信仰的人也會向前走。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰停下，信仰的人也會停下。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格的人們之所以在您的眼中嚮往著停滯，正是因為對耶拉岡德的信仰在蔓珠院手中停滯了千年！", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#9$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們遵循著某種約定俗成的規則畫地為牢，在這片雪山之中生活了上千年，不去探究外面的天地，不與外面的人交流。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#9$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而這種約定俗成，真的和信仰有關嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#9$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這難道不是只是蔓珠院的傲慢嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#9$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傲慢？不，不，它本該如此！", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#4$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒有什麼事本該如此。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有，那它一定只是從未有所改變。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該改變了，大長老。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_258_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女，不，你改變不了什麼的。", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#5$1"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信仰，咳咳......是謝拉格之所以是謝拉格的根基......", "name": "大長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_258_1#5$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會去和恩希歐迪斯對抗，但不是以您想要的方式。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知道我能不能成功。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，聖女既然從一開始就是蔓珠院用來引導民眾信仰的工具。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就讓這個工具真正發揮效果。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是聖女，但我不是蔓珠院的聖女，而是謝拉格的聖女。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會用我的方式去引導人民，讓他們能夠自由地去前進，去探究，去冒險。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而您，該休息了，大長老。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來人，將大長老扶回去。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅站起身，頭也不回地走向正殿門外。"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在她的背後，大長老坐在椅子上，注視著她的背影，他伸出手，似乎想要握住什麼，最終卻無力地垂下。"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他什麼也沒有握住。"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他永遠地停在了那裡，一如他夢中的謝拉格雪山。"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}